.DT
comment
Discworld playtester help
comment

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
comment - comment on a playtester's application.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
comment <name> <comment>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command will make a comment on a playtester application.  You can use this 
to record personal opinions, observations, queries or worries.  Please make any 
comments you feel are appropriate, whether positive or negative.

All comments about a particular applicant will be visible to the PT Exec who 
conducts their interview, but the originator of the comment will remain 
anonymous.  The Lord and deputies of the playtester domain will see the comments 
and their originators.
.SH Examples
.SI 5
> comment drakkos He smells of fish.
.EI

.SH See also
query applicants
.SP 5 5
.EP
